description.plain: The track was first hinted at in an infomercial for the album posted to her team’s social media accounts. A glitch in the video revealed four additional tracks that weren’t initially on the album. Upon the album’s release, it was revealed that each vinyl variant contained a hidden track. “girl i’ve always been” is currently only available on “GUTS (S purple vinyl).”
